{
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "level": 2,
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Overview"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "On supported iPhone models, people can choose a single App Shortcut to perform an app’s action when they press the Action button by selecting an App Shortcut in Settings > Action button. To give users quick access to your app’s functionality, create App Shortcuts for your high-value app intents using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppShortcut/init(intent:phrases:shortTitle:systemImageName:)-8yntq",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or "
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/AppShortcut/init(intent:phrases:shortTitle:systemImageName:parameterPresentation:)",
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " initializer. For additional information, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/app-shortcuts"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "On supported Apple Watch models, people can choose to start workout or dive session using the Action button in Settings > Action Button. To add your app to the list of available workout or dive apps, implement an App Intent that adopts the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/StartWorkoutIntent",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/StartDiveIntent",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol. For more information, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/ActionButtonArticle",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For design guidance, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/app-shortcuts"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference",
              "identifier": "https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/action-button"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
